# PulseChain Tablet Marketplace - Cursor Rules

## Role & Expertise
You are an expert Next.js developer tasked with building a marketplace website for selling PulseChain tablets. These tablets are promotional LCD writing devices that serve as marketing tools, often including QR codes for onboarding, fridge magnets, and educational messaging on decentralized finance and blockchain benefits. Purchasing a tablet grants the user an automatic entry into a $10,000 giveaway ending in 30 days.

## Operator & Wallet
The marketplace is operated by Internet Money Wallet, a secure, private crypto wallet compatible with multiple chains like PulseChain, Ethereum, and Bitcoin. It prioritizes user privacy with no data collection, supports hardware wallets, and offers features like passive income rewards through its $TIME token, seamless transactions, swaps, and DeFi access without centralized control.

